      <title>墨西哥选举法院确认莫雷纳在国会的实力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/mexico-s-electoral-court-confirms-morena-s-strength-in-congress</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥最高选举法院确认，执政党联盟将在众议院保持绝对多数，并且在六月大选后仅差几个席位就能在参议院取得同样的结果。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/mexico-s-electoral-court-confirms-morena-s-strength-in-congress</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 15:31:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纽森将决定是否为加州无证移民提供住房贷款援助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/california-s-home-loan-help-for-undocumented-immigrants-goes-to-newsom-s-desk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加州立法者已向州长加文·纽瑟姆提交了一份法案，该法案将扩大由州政府支持的首付援助计划，以惠及想要买房的无证移民。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/california-s-home-loan-help-for-undocumented-immigrants-goes-to-newsom-s-desk</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 15:24:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>致命袭击后德国加强武器和驱逐规定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/germany-tightens-weapons-deportation-rules-after-fatal-attack</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在上周发生致命的持刀袭击事件后，德国总理奥拉夫·朔尔茨领导的执政联盟同意了一揽子计划，旨在加强对刀具等武器的监管，并降低驱逐犯罪寻求庇护者的门槛。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/germany-tightens-weapons-deportation-rules-after-fatal-attack</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 15:19:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>赞比亚计划让国有企业拥有 30% 的关键矿产矿权</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/zambia-plans-state-firm-to-own-30-of-critical-minerals-mines</link>
      <description><![CDATA[赞比亚计划成立一家投资公司，控制未来矿山至少 30% 的关键矿产产量。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/zambia-plans-state-firm-to-own-30-of-critical-minerals-mines</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 14:53:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普称将宣布一项计划，让美国成为“加密之都”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/trump-says-he-ll-announce-a-plan-to-make-us-the-crypto-capital-of-the-planet</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普似乎正在更深入地涉足数字资产世界，他表示将公布计划，确保美国成为“全球加密之都”。]]></description>
